## Agent Rules (Global + Project)
- Global rules: `~/.grok-cli/agents/rules/`
- Project rules: `<project>/.agents/rules/`
- Loaded via `context::ContextEngine::load_agent_rules()`
- Merge logic: global first, project overrides same filename
- See: `skills/rules.rs` and `context/agent_rules.rs`

